				"§7  2. Place it inline on a §6Shaft§7 between power source and consumer."
				"§7  3. Wire a §6Redstone Torch or Lever§7 to the Clutch's side."
				"§7  4. When the redstone is ON, Clutch disconnects → downstream stops."
				""
				"§a► Task: Checkmark when a Clutch is installed and responding to redstone."
