				"§7  3. The Motor converts FE input → SU output on its shaft."
				"§7  4. Connect that shaft to your kinetic network."
				""
				"§eFE vs SU reminder:§r"
				"§7• §6FE§7 = universal power currency (most mods use this)."
				"§7• §6SU§7 = Create's physical stress/torque system."
				"§7• Create: New Age's Motors bridge between them."
