				"§7• Each tool slot shows its §6Head§7, §6Hilt§7, and §6Handle§7 separately."
				"§7• Clicking a component allows you to swap it for a different material."
				"§7• Higher-tier materials (Brass, Andesite Alloy from Create) unlock"
				"§7  special §epas bonuses§7 — speed near machines, durability in combat."
				""
				"§eTool types available:§r"
				"§7• §6Modular Sword§7 — main combat weapon, upgradeable to late-game tier."
				"§7• §6Modular Pickaxe§7 — primary mining tool, components affect speed."
				"§7• §6Modular Axe§7 — utility and combat, Andesite head is excellent."
				"§7• §6Modular Shovel§7 — terrain work with terrain-specific bonuses."
				"§7• §6Modular Bow§7 — ranged, upgradeable draw speed and damage."
				""
				"§eTip:§r §7Check §6Jade§7 on any Tetra tool — it shows current component"
				"§7stats and experience towards the next level."
				""
				"§a► Task: Have 1 Tetra Modular Workbench. Not consumed."
			]
